ote><blockquote>羅莽360<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n羅莽kick</blockquote><br />\n羅莽連彈"},{"pid":"190b748b46cf6d261150dcaf2dbb487bbc1f6b63","tid":160704,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T06:31:08.000Z","msg":"想睇佢多過膠面"},{"pid":"170813f7dacef4cd1a277477117f2c46874b6e73","tid":160704,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T06:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇過達哥訪問羅師傅條片<br />\n覺得羅師傅好有大俠feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又謙虛又友善</blockquote><br />\n達哥仲同佢過幾招tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45912569dfb7221c86bbac1be371d814b60c4ca5","tid":160704,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T06:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我頂撚死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9364b013d369021484a13317afa3887f1494ae","tid":160704,"uid":2936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T06:37:48.000Z","msg":"羅莽世界"},{"pid":"bf6a3edfc9ea93fbfec5cbc50a3bcc3c8c46d941","tid":160704,"uid":15339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T06:37:55.000Z","msg":"lawcfu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}